â€¢ Forwarding ğŸšš â€” FRAP 11; monitor completeness.
â€¢ Appendix/Excerpts ğŸ“š â€” FRAP 30/local rules: focused, indexed, with pinâ€‘cites.
ğŸ“ Assignment
