ğŸ“– Lesson Content
â€¢ Why Archive? ğŸ¯ â€” Memory (prevents revisionism), Leverage (invites oversight), Safety (antiâ€‘spoliation), and Teaching (others can replicate).
â€¢ What to Preserve ğŸ“¦ â€” Filings, orders, docket prints, clerk emails/returns, carrier receipts, portal confirmations, call logs, transcripts/transcript orders, declarations, processâ€‘server affidavits, timeâ€‘stamped screenshots, and press correspondence.
