â€¢ Pattern Recognition ğŸ“Š â€” Turn events into data: table of 'silence,' 'return,' 'mislabel,' 'noâ€‘ruling' with dates, actors, outcomes; chart frequency and latency. Convert the table to a declaration + timeline exhibit for filings.
